            "creation_date": 1564476389,
            "body": "<p>Assuming you have an instance of <code>CodecRegistry<\/code>, you can convert <code>BsonDocument<\/code> to <code>Document<\/code> and vice-versa using this adapter:<\/p>\n\n<pre class=\"lang-java prettyprint-override\"><code>public class DocumentAdapter {\n    private final CodecRegistry registry;\n    private final Codec&lt;Document&gt; codec;\n\n    public DocumentAdapter(CodecRegistry registry) {\n        this.registry = registry;\n        this.codec = registry.get(Document.class);\n    }\n\n    public Document fromBson(BsonDocument bson) {\n        return codec.decode(bson.asBsonReader(), DecoderContext.builder().build());\n    }\n\n    public BsonDocument toBson(Document document) {\n        return document.toBsonDocument(BsonDocument.class, registry);\n    }\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
            "answer_id": 57267705,
            "question_id": 49262903
        },
        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://i.sstatic.net/l4jLj.jpg?s=256",
                "account_id": 186461,
                "user_type": "registered",
                "user_id": 423868,
                "link": "https://stackoverflow.com/users/423868/georgy-gobozov",
                "reputation": 13731,
                "display_name": "Georgy Gobozov",
                "accept_rate": 65
            },
            "content_license": "CC BY-SA 4.0",
            "score": 4,
            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1596693448,
            "creation_date": 1596693448,
            "body": "<pre><code>public static Document bsonToDocument(BsonDocument bsonDocument) {\n    DocumentCodec codec = new DocumentCodec();\n    DecoderContext decoderContext = DecoderContext.builder().build();\n    return codec.decode(new BsonDocumentReader(bsonDocument), decoderContext);\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
            "answer_id": 63277658,
            "question_id": 49262903
        },
        {
            "owner": {
